rows.label: qst004002_msg0001
rows.name:
I saw something!
At Zeno's Deadbole!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0002
rows.name:
There's nothing there normally,
but it shone when I passed by lately!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0003
rows.name:
I'll bet anything that someone took
a big sword, broke the crane with it,
then hid it there! Oh my days, so scary!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0004
rows.name:
And now of all times, the Superbian
soldiers just sit around? Disgraceful!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0101
rows.name:
That Superbia lot say they're here
to protect Gula... What a load of
guff! They haven't protected me once!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0102
rows.name:
That's like my husband, promising on
our wedding day he'd tell me he loves
me every morning...

rows.label: qst004002_msg0103
rows.name:
Well, whaddya know? He lasted three
days! You call that a good husband?
Because I don't!
